* free SRM contract converter
  cl_mmbsi_cc_conv=>cleanup( ).                             "1620881

* cleanup database utility
  IF for_me59n EQ mmpur_no.
    cl_mmpur_out_db_utility=>cleanup( ).                      "2038808
